I've never been out to Temperantia
myself, so I dunno if this is true, but...

rows.label: tlk43320242_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard they got some crazy-strong
monster called Tyrannotitan Kurodil
sealed away over there.

rows.label: tlk43320242_04_msg0004
rows.name:
About 300 years ago, a coupla hundred
Ice-type Blades teamed up and put the
seal on him, they say.

rows.label: tlk43320242_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I heard they got loads of nasty
monsters like that over there.

rows.label: tlk43320242_04_msg0006
rows.name:
There's no people living there.
It's a desolate place.

rows.label: tlk43320242_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Probably 'cos of all the monsters,
I'll bet.
